INSERT INTO committee (
                id,
                name_nl,
                name_en,
                description_nl,
                description_en,
                image,
                created,
                updated
            )
            VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6, now(), now())
            RETURNING
                id,
                name_nl,
                name_en,
                description_nl,
                description_en,
                created,
                updated,
                image
